flowchart TD
  subgraph Presentation ["Presentation Layer"]
    UI[SystemAdminUI]
  end

  subgraph Business ["Business Layer"]
    Controller[SystemAdminController]
    Facade[SecurityFacade]
  end

  subgraph Domain ["Domain Layer"]
    User[UserAccount]
    Role[UserRole]
    Log[OperationLog]
  end

  subgraph Infrastructure ["Infrastructure Layer"]
    UserRepo[UserAccountRepository]
    RoleRepo[UserRoleRepository]
    LogRepo[OperationLogRepository]
  end

  Presentation -.->|uses| Business
  Business -.->|manipulates| Domain
  Business -.->|uses| Infrastructure
  Infrastructure -.->|persists| Domain
